{"id":438615380,"lang":"java","time":"1 year, 1 month","timestamp":1609800239,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"1 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/438615380/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Sqrt(x)","memory":"36.1 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int mySqrt(int x) {\n        if (x < 2) return x;\n        \n        long num;\n        int pivot, left = 2, right = x / 2;\n        \n        while (left <= right) {\n            pivot = left + (right - left) / 2;\n            num = (long) pivot * pivot;\n            if (num > x) {\n                right = pivot - 1;\n            } else if (num < x) {\n                left = pivot + 1;\n            } else return pivot;\n        }\n        \n        return right;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"sqrtx"}
